{"tid":416717,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【極緊急】政府擬以「參與恐怖主義」為名禁市民離境 諮詢今日5時完結","createTime":"2017-09-28T04:01:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-30T10:38:12.000Z","uid":79563,"like":5,"dislike":37,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"0b7afc61bfe9004aa4044000119c2fcdd952215b","tid":416717,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T04:01:02.000Z","msg":"SOURCE: <a href=\"https://prism.news/ShowArt.php?ref=20170928001\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fprism.news%2FShowArt.php%3Fref%3D20170928001&d=iSYwik3gVh0G1Y9y2f78fRxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=b7ae41f7\" target=\"_blank\">https://prism.news/ShowArt.php?ref=20170928001</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://prism.news/images/000001_JPG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fprism.news%2Fimages%2F000001_JPG.jpg&h=04ddcb85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港立法會正就《2017年聯合國(反恐怖主義措施)(修訂)條例草案》進行公眾諮詢，其中保安局建議立法「禁止任何香港永久性居民離開或登上運輸工具意圖離開香港或香港以外地方前往外國，以作出、籌劃、籌備或參與恐怖主義行為，或提供或接受恐怖主義培訓」。<br />\n<br />\n保安局表示曾於2017年3月9日向香港律師會作簡介，而最後共接獲 1 0 份意見書，全部表示普遍支持。<br />\n<br />\n立法會秘書處助理法律顧問李凱詩指，條例草案其中一個目的是「令若干紀律部隊的人員能夠為執行有關禁制而行使他們現有的法定權力」。<br />\n<br />\n然而，有關條例或會抵觸市民出入境自由。<br />\n<br />\n另一方面，立法會文件顯示，政府或會向法庭申請指明某人為恐怖分子。<br />\n<br />\n會議議程及相關文件：<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.legco.gov.hk/yr16-17/chinese/bc/bc59/general/bc59.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.legco.gov.hk%2Fyr16-17%2Fchinese%2Fbc%2Fbc59%2Fgeneral%2Fbc59.htm&d=iSYwik3gVh0G1Y9y2f78fRxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=2265dd2b\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.legco.gov.hk/yr16-17/chinese/bc/bc59/general/bc59.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n有興趣的人士或團體請於2017年9月28日（星期四）下午5時或之前提交網上回覆表格和意見書。<br />\n<br />\n意見書可以透過電郵、郵遞或傳真方式遞交，詳情如下：<br />\n<br />\n郵遞地址：\t<br />\n香港中區<br />\n立法會道1號<br />\n立法會綜合大樓<br />\n立法會秘書處<br />\n《2017年聯合國(反恐怖主義措施)(修訂)條例草案》委員會秘書<br />\n<br />\n傳真號碼： 2185 7845<br />\n電話號碼： 3919 3226 或 3919 3209<br />\n電郵地址： [url]bc_59_16@legco.gov.hk[/url]"},{"pid":"2543d5b6c0636bb69aaf136e600a982d7ca80d9e","tid":416717,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T04:02:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a78328eca9d0d0cf80418d98a58bcc75409aad3","tid":416717,"uid":28831,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T04:04:29.000Z","msg":"係就快<br />\n無得旅行仲唔暴動？"},{"pid":"1fc49568771e5af8a4ad1b879650fed036e80e14","tid":416717,"uid":44461,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T04:13:44.000Z","msg":"痴撚線 但真係過硬"},{"pid":"95d8819191752ab98cb8ccf18a615e940b09f7d5","tid":416717,"uid":5686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T04:15:26.000Z","msg":"正！誠哥想移民？"},{"pid":"9088474a3d57481250b78d04980af90a32bafff7","tid":416717,"uid":25866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T04:34:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4965706ef566e012d4fb7838261281a50a569565","tid":416717,"uid":5056,"like":3,"dislike":9,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T04:34:34.000Z","msg":"個人覺得個原意係無問題，英國都有類似措施:<br />\nNew power to confiscate terror suspects' passports - BBC News<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/news/uk-22297436\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fuk-22297436&d=iSYwik3gVh0G1Y9y2f78fRxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=240507ca\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fuk-22297436&h=46eeed68\" target=\"_blank\">www.bbc.com/news/uk-22297436</a><br />\n<br />\n但問題係宜家呢個政府咁嘅民望，點執行都會比人插"},{"pid":"5d3b5ef84b15b2d2eefb488d78c92522bf1c3626","tid":416717,"uid":4664